pyweblog-0.6.1:
-----------
1) change to google_appengine_1.2.2.
2) add "ccluck" (thanks to xiaoci).
3) add ip lookup, based on ip location database "QQWrp.Dat", minor changes to pyip.py.
4) add Google custom search element (http://www.google.com/coop/manage/cse/)
5) add widgets: google map/google conversation/google YouTube news/google friend connect.

pyweblog-0.6.0:
-----------
1) menu part: current page was highlighted.
2) new post: textarea's font defaults to 16px, (file
"/scripts/tiny_mce/themes/advanced/skins/default/content.css").
3) changed the length of input text box.
4) added a search box.
5) added MM:DD tag before the title of every passage.
6) showed readers number
7) changed the original way of comment, logging was not needed; also showing comments with cycled colored.
8) supported IP tracks.
9) restricted line length in sidebar, text overflowed would be hidden, not
wrapped.
10) passage content's font became larger.
11) supported page-break.
12) allowed blog content contains <span style=...> tag.
13) fixed tag bug in Links widget.
14) Del all was supported in Upload files.
15) picture insertion was supported when posting blog.
16) change index.yaml, added autogenerated part
17) dynamic sitemap.txt file

